      "start": 614.92,
      "end": 616.28,
      "text": "역시 good teacher입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.68,
      "end": 617.18,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 617.48,
      "end": 618.06,
      "text": "자, 이 내용"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.06,
      "end": 619.02,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 619.7,
      "end": 620.42,
      "text": "Why did you"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.42,
      "end": 621.46,
      "text": "run out of my class?"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.96,
      "end": 622.8,
      "text": "I got scared."
    },
    {
      "start": 623.42,
      "end": 623.9,
      "text": "Of what?"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.68,
      "end": 625.32,
      "text": "Other kids?"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.06,
      "end": 626.4,
      "text": "Maybe."
    },
    {
      "start": 627.06,
      "end": 627.58,
      "text": "Or maybe"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.58,
      "end": 628.62,
      "text": "finding out that I'm bad."
    },
    {
      "start": 629.28,
      "end": 629.9,
      "text": "Do you know what"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.9,
      "end": 630.92,
      "text": "Bowie said about"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.92,
      "end": 631.34,
      "text": "Bob Dylan?"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.9,
      "end": 632.62,
      "text": "A voice like"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.62,
      "end": 633.74,
      "text": "sand and glue."
    },
    {
      "start": 633.74,
      "end": 635.36,
      "text": "There are plenty"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.36,
      "end": 636.02,
      "text": "of pretty voices"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.02,
      "end": 637.14,
      "text": "with nothing to say."
    },
    {
      "start": 637.72,
      "end": 638.18,
      "text": "Do you have"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.18,
      "end": 639.14,
      "text": "something to say?"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.58,
      "end": 640.42,
      "text": "I think so."
    },
    {
      "start": 642.01,
      "end": 643.21,
      "text": "자, 오늘 이렇게"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.21,
      "end": 644.19,
      "text": "장면을 들어보면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.19,
      "end": 645.21,
      "text": "다시 한 번 느끼지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.21,
      "end": 646.19,
      "text": "It's really important"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.19,
      "end": 648.03,
      "text": "to meet a good teacher"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.03,
      "end": 649.35,
      "text": "in our life."
    },
    {
      "start": 649.41,
      "end": 650.51,
      "text": "A teacher can change"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.51,
      "end": 651.01,
      "text": "your life."
    },
    {
      "start": 651.01,
      "end": 651.29,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 651.43,
      "end": 652.21,
      "text": "The right teacher"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.21,
      "end": 653.95,
      "text": "who says the right things."
    },
    {
      "start": 654.09,
      "end": 654.35,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 654.51,
      "end": 655.75,
      "text": "정말 좋은 선생님을"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.75,
      "end": 656.85,
      "text": "인생에서 만나는 것이"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.85,
      "end": 658.13,
      "text": "얼마나 중요한 일인지"
    },
    {
      "start": 658.13,
      "end": 659.91,
      "text": "오늘도 다시 깨닫게 되네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 660.11,
      "end": 661.33,
      "text": "오늘은 조크쌤과"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.33,
      "end": 662.63,
      "text": "맞습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 662.63,
      "end": 664.39,
      "text": "그냥 good teachers 되도록"
    },
    {
      "start": 664.39,
      "end": 665.81,
      "text": "앞으로도 노력 많이 하겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 666.35,
      "end": 667.47,
      "text": "I'll try my best."
    },
    {
      "start": 667.77,
      "end": 669.53,
      "text": "우리 내일 다시 만날게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 669.75,
      "end": 670.25,
      "text": "See you tomorrow."
    }
  ]
}